ng a GeoJSON source is not compatible with using shared cache and generated IDs."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It is important to ensure that every feature in the GeoJSON style source, as well as the newly added"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"feature, has a unique ID (or a unique promote ID if in use). Failure to provide unique IDs will result"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"in a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"map-loading-error"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The method allows the user to provide a data ID, which will be returned as the ","type":"text"},{"code":"dataId","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" parameter in the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"source-data-loaded"},{"type":"text","text":" event. However, it’s important to note that multiple partial updates can be queued"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"for the same GeoJSON source when ongoing source parsing is taking place. In these cases, the partial"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"updates will be applied to the source in batches. Only the data ID provided in the most recent call within","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"each batch will be included in the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"source-data-loaded"},{"type":"text","text":" event. If no data ID is provided in the most recent"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"call, the data ID in the ","type":"text"},{"code":"source-data-loaded","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"event will be null.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"Note","style":"note","type":"aside"},{"name":"Throws","type":"aside","style":"note","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":""},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.mapbox.MapboxMaps\/documentation\/MapboxMaps\/StyleError","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" if there is a problem updating features in the source."}],"ty